      "title": "Dialog promotes best data plans for entire family",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Dialog Home Broadband has introduced exclusive affordable Data Plans for the entire family.",
        "For just Rs. 1,299 + taxes, you can now enjoy unlimited data for Netflix and the ViU App, along with 100GB of data for Apple TV, Amazon Prime and Spotify for a full 30 days.",
        "If you\u2019d like to make that even more affordable or flexible to meet your requirements, you can enjoy the seven-day plan for only Rs. 499 + Taxes; with unlimited data for Netflix and the ViU App along with 20GB of data for Apple TV, Amazon Prime and Spotify. If you\u2019re more a music person than anything else, you can get 10GB of data for Spotify for 30 days at a very affordable Rs. 179 + taxes."
      ],
